title: Dwight Yoakam & The Babylonian Cowboys
itunes:title: Dwight Yoakam & The Babylonian Cowboys
description: Among the more uproarious of SNAP sessions, Dwight Yoakam brought his merry band of Babylonian Cowboys to SNAP in July 1986. In addition to playing a full set of rip-roaring country and bluegrass, Yoakam and his band engage Deirdre in a stream of relentless banter and convivial shit-talking. One for the books.
